{"id": "86205", "revid": "40389549", "url": "https://wowpedia.fandom.com/wiki?curid=86205", "title": "Healing Focus (shaman talent)", "text": "Healing Focus is a &lt;a href=\"Shaman\"&gt;Shaman&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"talent\"&gt;talent&lt;/a&gt; in the &lt;a href=\"Shaman%20talents%23Restoration\"&gt;Restoration&lt;/a&gt; tree. It greatly reduces the &lt;a href=\"pushback\"&gt;pushback&lt;/a&gt; suffered when you take damage while casting a healing spell.\nNotes.\nThe pushback duration reduction from this talent stacks with other similar effects, such as &lt;a href=\"Earth%20Shield\"&gt;Earth Shield&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Concentration%20Aura\"&gt;Concentration Aura&lt;/a&gt;. The effects are additive, and it is possible to reach 100% pushback reduction. Combining three points in Healing Focus with Earth Shield will make the shaman immune to pushback.\nNote that pushback is not the same thing as &lt;a href=\"Interrupt%23Interruption%20Caused%20by%20Counterspell%20Effects\"&gt;interruption&lt;/a&gt;. Healing Focus will not give any protection against abilities such as &lt;a href=\"Kick\"&gt;Kick&lt;/a&gt; or &lt;a href=\"Counterspell\"&gt;Counterspell&lt;/a&gt;. Instead, the Restoration talent &lt;a href=\"Focused%20Mind%20%28Shaman%29\"&gt;Focused Mind&lt;/a&gt; reduces the duration of such effects."}
