{"id": "43168", "revid": "49740203", "url": "https://wowpedia.fandom.com/wiki?curid=43168", "title": "Healing Grace", "text": "Healing Grace is a &lt;a href=\"Shaman\"&gt;Shaman&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"talent\"&gt;talent&lt;/a&gt; in the &lt;a href=\"Shaman%20talents%23Restoration\"&gt;Restoration&lt;/a&gt; tree. It reduces the &lt;a href=\"threat\"&gt;threat&lt;/a&gt; generated by all healing spells and gives a chance for your &lt;a href=\"buff\"&gt;buff&lt;/a&gt;s to resist &lt;a href=\"Dispel\"&gt;Dispel&lt;/a&gt; effects.\nNotes.\nWith the changes to tank threat generation in patch 3.0, the usefulness of the threat reduction part of this talent is greatly reduced, and is generally considered to be unnecessary. The main use of this talent is currently the dispel resistance, which is very useful in &lt;a href=\"PvP\"&gt;PvP&lt;/a&gt;."}
