{"id": "157020", "revid": "49740203", "url": "https://wowpedia.fandom.com/wiki?curid=157020", "title": "Heart Candy", "text": "The comment on Heart Candy can have one of eight different flavor phrases:\nSource.\nHeart Candy can be found inside a . Each time the bag is used, one of the eight \"Heart Candy\" items is created. In addition to the saying, it also says &lt;Made by Name-of-Character&gt;, the character who opened the \"Bag of Candies\" creating the item. \nAchievements.\nThe World Event achievement for the &lt;a href=\"Love%20is%20in%20the%20Air\"&gt;Love is in the Air&lt;/a&gt; event requires you to eat all eight of these items . The odds are good that it will take more than one \"Bag of Candies\" to complete the achievement. This is in turn part of the &lt;a href=\"Fool%20For%20Love\"&gt;Fool For Love&lt;/a&gt; meta-achievement.\nAs these candy hearts can be traded and auctioned off, it is not truly necessary to open bags of candies to complete this achievement.\nProbability.\nThe odds of creating any one of the eight on any use of the bag appears to be equal, one in eight of any of them, and after considerable digging, one comment on WoWHead (for the spell, Create Heart Candy, #26678) backs this up, but there does not seem to be a reliable source to verify this with.\nFiguring out how long it takes (how many bags, 10 sample each) is intractable if you view it as a and attempt to follow each branching probability tree. However, the achievement can be viewed as a series of eight s; each characterized by a between outcomes \"new candy\" and \"no new candy\". Each binomial distribution has an expected time to success of 1/p, p being 8/8, 7/8, 6/8, 5/8, 4/8, 3/8, 2/8, and 1/8, and the expected times are additive, 8/8 + 8/7 + 8/6 + 8/5 + 8/4 + 8/3 + 8/2 + 8/1 . The results is that it on the average takes just over two bags (about 21\u00be samples) to complete this achievement. \nThis can be misleading; there is no cap on how long this can take; the distribution of samples to complete is weighted toward the low end with a shrinking number requiring more and more samples. Think of a long crane arm with a heavy counterweight. The bulk of the people attempting this achievement will complete it with only two bags and a few people will take much longer."}
{"id": "65659", "revid": "49740203", "url": "https://wowpedia.fandom.com/wiki?curid=65659", "title": "Heart Fire Warhammer", "text": "Heart Fire Warhammer is a &lt;a href=\"two-hand\"&gt;two-hand&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"mace\"&gt;mace&lt;/a&gt;. It gives bonuses to &lt;a href=\"strength\"&gt;strength&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"stamina\"&gt;stamina&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"intellect\"&gt;intellect&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"spell%20power\"&gt;spell power&lt;/a&gt;, and &lt;a href=\"mana%20regeneration\"&gt;mana regeneration&lt;/a&gt;. It has a natural fiery red &lt;a href=\"weapon%20glow\"&gt;weapon glow&lt;/a&gt;.\nSource.\nThis item drops from &lt;a href=\"Omor%20the%20Unscarred\"&gt;Omor the Unscarred&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a href=\"Hellfire%20Ramparts\"&gt;Hellfire Ramparts&lt;/a&gt;. It has a Low (15% - 24%) Drop Chance."}
{"id": "635936", "revid": "38791128", "url": "https://wowpedia.fandom.com/wiki?curid=635936", "title": "Heart Forge", "text": "The Heart Forge is found in the &lt;a href=\"Chamber%20of%20Heart\"&gt;Chamber of Heart&lt;/a&gt;. It is used to infuse the &lt;a href=\"Heart%20of%20Azeroth\"&gt;Heart of Azeroth&lt;/a&gt; with &lt;a href=\"Azerite%20essence\"&gt;Azerite essence&lt;/a&gt;s.\nActivating the Heart Forge was &lt;a href=\"MOTHER\"&gt;MOTHER&lt;/a&gt;'s idea; she detected that &lt;a href=\"Azeroth%20%28titan%29\"&gt;Azeroth&lt;/a&gt; was still dying, and that something needed to be done to further help her. After some calculations, MOTHER concluded that infusing the Heart of Azeroth with magical essences would fortify it and, in turn, the planet herself.\nUnlocking the Heart Forge.\nIn order to unlock the Heart Forge and gain access to the essence system, you need to complete a series of requirements:\nSlots.\nWith the Heart Forge unlocked, you can either interact with the Heart Forge or right-click on the &lt;a href=\"Heart%20of%20Azeroth\"&gt;Heart of Azeroth&lt;/a&gt; to view the essence interface. It contains slots that can be activated at the Heart Forge after reaching certain Heart of Azeroth levels. Note that &lt;a href=\"The%20Heart%20Forge\"&gt;The Heart Forge&lt;/a&gt; immediately raises your Heart of Azeroth level to 50, allowing use of the major slot right away."}
