{"id": "279915", "revid": "40389549", "url": "https://wowpedia.fandom.com/wiki?curid=279915", "title": "Desolation Hold", "text": "Desolation Hold is a &lt;a href=\"Horde\"&gt;Horde&lt;/a&gt; fortress in &lt;a href=\"Southern%20Barrens\"&gt;Southern Barrens&lt;/a&gt; located on the western side of the &lt;a href=\"Battlescar\"&gt;Battlescar&lt;/a&gt;, with the &lt;a href=\"Alliance\"&gt;Alliance&lt;/a&gt; outpost &lt;a href=\"Fort%20Triumph\"&gt;Fort Triumph&lt;/a&gt; on the eastern side. &lt;a href=\"Warlord%20Gar%27dul\"&gt;Warlord Gar'dul&lt;/a&gt; had Desolation Hold constructed over a &lt;a href=\"Silithid\"&gt;Silithid&lt;/a&gt; colony, known as the &lt;a href=\"Field%20of%20Giants\"&gt;Field of Giants&lt;/a&gt;, over &lt;a href=\"Crawgol\"&gt;Crawgol&lt;/a&gt;'s objections.\nWarlord Gar'dul, who was in charge of the Horde in the region, failed to live up to the expectations of &lt;a href=\"Garrosh%20Hellscream\"&gt;Warchief Garrosh&lt;/a&gt;, because of this he has sent &lt;a href=\"Warlord%20Bloodhilt\"&gt;Warlord Bloodhilt&lt;/a&gt; to investigate the situation and solve the problem. Warlord Bloodhilt, having solved the issue, took command of the fortress until he &lt;a href=\"Dominance%20Offensive\"&gt;joined&lt;/a&gt; the war effort in &lt;a href=\"Pandaria\"&gt;Pandaria&lt;/a&gt; and relocated to &lt;a href=\"Domination%20Point\"&gt;Domination Point&lt;/a&gt;, where he met his end.\nBy the time of the &lt;a href=\"Fourth%20War\"&gt;Fourth War&lt;/a&gt;, command of Desolation Hold belonged to &lt;a href=\"Crawgol\"&gt;Warlord Crawgol&lt;/a&gt;. The hold came under attack by Alliance forces that were sent to attack in order to reestablish Fort Triumph."}
