{"id": "13954", "revid": "22514", "url": "https://wowpedia.fandom.com/wiki?curid=13954", "title": "Desperate Prayer", "text": "Desperate Prayer is a &lt;a href=\"priest\"&gt;priest&lt;/a&gt; ability. It is an instant self-only heal that costs no mana to use, healing the caster for 25% of their total health.\nTips and tactics.\nDesperate Prayer heals for a notable amount, and most importantly for free. Since it is not affected by the GCD, it can also be used simultaneous to other heals to provide significant instant protection. Priests can save it for truly dangerous moments where it can be used at a moment's notice, or simply use it regularly to save mana and globals."}
