{"id": "301555", "revid": "41372093", "url": "https://wowpedia.fandom.com/wiki?curid=301555", "title": "Raz Skullcrusher", "text": "Raz Skullcrusher is the bodyguard of &lt;a href=\"Pip%20Quickwit\"&gt;Pip Quickwit&lt;/a&gt;.\nBlackrock Caverns instance.\n&lt;a href=\"Twilight%27s%20Hammer\"&gt;Twilight's Hammer&lt;/a&gt; cultists ambush Raz and Pip immediately upon their exiting the &lt;a href=\"Pip%27s%20Mole%20Machine\"&gt;mole machine&lt;/a&gt; they use to travel to Blackrock Caverns. While Pip ran away, Raz was beaten unconscious and taken to the \"Chamber of Incineration\".\nHe is eventually found, being held prisoner by &lt;a href=\"Rom%27ogg%20Bonecrusher\"&gt;Rom'ogg Bonecrusher&lt;/a&gt;, and transformed into a &lt;a href=\"dire%20orc\"&gt;dire orc&lt;/a&gt;. When the adventuring party frees him, he starts wading through the cultists in front of them, somehow getting past the bosses that you have to fight. Eventually, he is slain by &lt;a href=\"Ascendant%20Lord%20Obsidius\"&gt;Ascendant Lord Obsidius&lt;/a&gt;, just before the party gets there, leaving Pip to mourn his friend.\nRelatives.\nHe may be related to &lt;a href=\"Nekros%20Skullcrusher\"&gt;Nekros&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Nek%27rosh%20Skullcrusher\"&gt;Nek'rosh Skullcrusher&lt;/a&gt;, the former leaders of the &lt;a href=\"Dragonmaw%20clan\"&gt;Dragonmaw clan&lt;/a&gt;. Thus Raz may be a member of the clan as well."}
