{"id": "588235", "revid": "42014766", "url": "https://wowpedia.fandom.com/wiki?curid=588235", "title": "Razgaji", "text": "Razgaji is the leader of a &lt;a href=\"Scorched%20Sands%20tribe\"&gt;tribe&lt;/a&gt; of &lt;a href=\"Zandalari%20troll\"&gt;Zandalari troll&lt;/a&gt; exiles at the &lt;a href=\"Scorched%20Sands%20Outpost\"&gt;Scorched Sands Outpost&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a href=\"Vol%27dun\"&gt;Vol'dun&lt;/a&gt;. He used to be a member of &lt;a href=\"Mojambo\"&gt;Mojambo&lt;/a&gt;'s gang of thugs but left in the hopes of a second chance at an honest life. Shortly after an &lt;a href=\"adventurer\"&gt;adventurer&lt;/a&gt; arrives at the outpost, Mojambo and his henchmons threaten the &lt;a href=\"Scorched%20Sands%20Arena\"&gt;Scorched Sands Arena&lt;/a&gt;, and Razgaji asks the adventurer to back him up as he convinces the rival gang to leave. Mojambo complies but promises to come back and kill Razgaji.\nRazgaji sends the hero to assist &lt;a href=\"Mugjabu\"&gt;Mugjabu&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Sezahjin\"&gt;Sezahjin&lt;/a&gt; in order to prepare the outpost for Mojambo's attack. After the adventurer does so, they hear from &lt;a href=\"Zauljin\"&gt;Zauljin&lt;/a&gt; that Mojambo has hired &lt;a href=\"Tongo\"&gt;Tongo&lt;/a&gt;'s gang to help him in the attack on the outpost, prompting Razgaji to send the adventurer to take Tongo's head and retrieve weapons and various stolen supplies from Tongo's crew. Just as the adventurer finishes arming the outcasts at the outpost with Tongo's weapons, Mojambo's gang attack the arena. The adventurer uses Tongo's head to challenge Mojambo to a duel that ends in the hostile gang leader's death, thus saving the outpost and Razgaji's outcasts."}
