{"id": "41616", "revid": "39299307", "url": "https://wowpedia.fandom.com/wiki?curid=41616", "title": "Razor Hill Grunt", "text": "Razor Hill Grunts are &lt;a href=\"orc\"&gt;orc&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"guard\"&gt;guard&lt;/a&gt;s located in the town of &lt;a href=\"Razor%20Hill\"&gt;Razor Hill&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a href=\"Durotar\"&gt;Durotar&lt;/a&gt;. They are stationed at the town entrance/exits, structures and patrol the streets. They are simple grunts that serve to protect Razor Hill citizens from the dangers in the environment such as boars and snakes as well as crush any sailors or marines that decide to launch an attack on Razor Hill from the Alliance fortress of &lt;a href=\"Tiragarde%20Keep\"&gt;Tiragarde Keep&lt;/a&gt;. They can provide directions to various locations.\nMists of Pandaria.\nEscalation.\n&lt;a href=\"Kor%27kron%20Overseer%20%28Durotar%29\"&gt;Kor'kron Overseer&lt;/a&gt;s have taken the place of Grunts in light of &lt;a href=\"Vol%27jin\"&gt;Vol'jin&lt;/a&gt;'s &lt;a href=\"Darkspear%20Rebellion\"&gt;rebellion&lt;/a&gt;. Upon conclusion of the events of &lt;a href=\"Battle%20of%20Razor%20Hill\"&gt;Battle of Razor Hill&lt;/a&gt;, the Overseers are replaced by &lt;a href=\"Darkspear%20Headhunter\"&gt;Darkspear Headhunter&lt;/a&gt;s.\nQuotes.\nWhat are you looking for?\n&lt;br&gt;\n&lt;br&gt;\n&lt;br&gt;\n&lt;br&gt;"}
