{"id": "38466", "revid": "46586549", "url": "https://wowpedia.fandom.com/wiki?curid=38466", "title": "Razorfen tribe", "text": "The Razorfen tribe is a &lt;a href=\"tribe\"&gt;tribe&lt;/a&gt; of &lt;a href=\"quilboar\"&gt;quilboar&lt;/a&gt; led by &lt;a href=\"Charlga%20Razorflank\"&gt;Charlga Razorflank&lt;/a&gt;.\nThe tribe controls both &lt;a href=\"Razorfen%20Kraul\"&gt;Razorfen Kraul&lt;/a&gt; and the &lt;a href=\"Razorfen%20Downs\"&gt;Razorfen Downs&lt;/a&gt; where &lt;a href=\"Agamaggan\"&gt;Agamaggan&lt;/a&gt; died. The quilboar are believed to be the offspring of &lt;a href=\"Agamaggan\"&gt;Agamaggan&lt;/a&gt;. Razorfen Kraul was conquered by &lt;a href=\"Charlga%20Razorflank\"&gt;Charlga Razorflank&lt;/a&gt;, who is now living deep inside. Within their lair they amassed their forces, threatening the land. The Razorfen tribe has driven the &lt;a href=\"tauren\"&gt;tauren&lt;/a&gt; away from southern &lt;a href=\"Barrens\"&gt;Barrens&lt;/a&gt;. The quilboar managed to capture &lt;a href=\"Willix%20the%20Importer\"&gt;Willix the Importer&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Henrig%20Lonebrow\"&gt;Henrig Lonebrow&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Heralath%20Fallowbrook\"&gt;Heralath Fallowbrook&lt;/a&gt;.\nAs stated by Charlga Razorflank, their \"New allies will avenge us\". The Razorfen seemed to have befriended the &lt;a href=\"Scourge\"&gt;Scourge&lt;/a&gt; in the Razorfen Downs, but the Scourge took them over, and forced them to move their capital into &lt;a href=\"Razorfen%20Kraul\"&gt;Razorfen Kraul&lt;/a&gt;. As such, they seem to be allied with &lt;a href=\"Death%27s%20Head%20tribe\"&gt;Death's Head tribe&lt;/a&gt; which is said to be led by Charlga.\nAt some point after the &lt;a href=\"Cataclysm%20%28event%29\"&gt;Cataclysm&lt;/a&gt;, a part of the Razorfen quilboar entered a truce with the &lt;a href=\"tauren\"&gt;tauren&lt;/a&gt; of the reclaimed &lt;a href=\"Freewind%20Post\"&gt;Freewind Post&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a href=\"Thousand%20Needles\"&gt;Thousand Needles&lt;/a&gt;. According to &lt;a href=\"Shagtusk\"&gt;Shagtusk&lt;/a&gt;, the tribe needed to destroy the unnatural magic of &lt;a href=\"Razorfen%20Downs\"&gt;Razorfen Downs&lt;/a&gt;. She hold Chugara and Blackthorn in low regards.\nIn the RPG.\nThe Razorfens are the most powerful &lt;a href=\"quilboar\"&gt;quilboar&lt;/a&gt; tribe in the land. They practice a shamanistic &lt;a href=\"magic\"&gt;magic&lt;/a&gt; and stage attacks on rival tribes and &lt;a href=\"Horde\"&gt;Horde&lt;/a&gt; villages."}
