{"id": "574870", "revid": "49740203", "url": "https://wowpedia.fandom.com/wiki?curid=574870", "title": "Razorfin Hunting Spear (quest)", "text": "Objectives.\nTake the spear to &lt;a href=\"Tired%20Shushen\"&gt;Tired Shushen&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a href=\"Krasarang%20Wilds\"&gt;Krasarang Wilds&lt;/a&gt;.\nDescription.\n&lt;This spear is razor sharp, though it has clearly seen many years of hunting in the open sea.\nThe shaft has been broken in several places and repaired with what materials were available at the time. From the variety of repair materials, you surmise that the &lt;a href=\"jinyu\"&gt;jinyu&lt;/a&gt; tribe you recently faced must travel extensively.\nThe friendly jinyu of &lt;a href=\"Pandaria\"&gt;Pandaria&lt;/a&gt; might know more about this strange tribe.&gt;\nRewards.\nYou will receive:\nCompletion.\nAh, yes, I do recognize this spear. You have encountered the Razorfin, then?\nThey are unique amongst Jinyu. Long ago the elder of the tribe was granted a vision of a great beast. So terrified was he that he named it \"Onoho,\" or \"Deep Shadow.\"\nHe dedicated his tribe to slaying the beast. They travel from island to island, never staying for long, in their endless quest. It is fascinating.\nI thank you for your visit. Some Azerite has washed ashore here, please take it, we have little use for it."}
