{"id": "570758", "revid": "39299307", "url": "https://wowpedia.fandom.com/wiki?curid=570758", "title": "Razorfin tribe", "text": "The Razorfin are a &lt;a href=\"tribe\"&gt;tribe&lt;/a&gt; and a &lt;a href=\"clan\"&gt;clan&lt;/a&gt; of &lt;a href=\"jinyu\"&gt;jinyu&lt;/a&gt; located on the &lt;a href=\"Rotting%20Mire\"&gt;Rotting Mire&lt;/a&gt;.\nThey are unique amongst jinyu. Long ago the elder of the tribe was granted a vision of a great beast. So terrified was he that he named it \"&lt;a href=\"Onoho\"&gt;Onoho&lt;/a&gt;,\" or \"Deep Shadow.\" He dedicated his tribe to slaying the beast. They travel from island to island, never staying for long, in their endless quest.\nSpeculation.\nOnoho may be &lt;a href=\"N%27Zoth\"&gt;N'Zoth&lt;/a&gt; as during the events in the &lt;a href=\"Eternal%20Palace\"&gt;Eternal Palace&lt;/a&gt; he takes the shape of a mass of black shadows. "}
